baseName.value: Shaped, cutted and welded steel FOR REINFORCED CONCRETE (Catania)

generalComment.value:
Data quality has been assessed and validated during data collection process.

According to ISO 14040 and 14044, allocation is avoided whenever possible by dividing the system into subsystems. When allocation cannot be avoided physical properties are used to drive flow analysis.

According to EN:15804 the applied cut-off criterion for mass and energy flows is 1%.

technologyDescriptionAndIncludedProcesse.value:
In general, the main components of the final product are: iron > 96%; alloying
elements (e.g. manganese, silicon, carbon) approx 2%; other elements (e.g.
copper, nickel, chromium), 100% complementary.
